@REMARK
@REMARK The Hebrew-Drawer
@REMARK

@NODE "Hebrew"

This drawer contains Hebrew fonts. Latin characters remain in positions 
32 - 127 and the Hebrew characters are from 192 - 224. Amiga user should
copy the keymap file to the DEVS:Keymaps directory and choose the "Hebrew"
keymap from "Input" in order to use the hebrew character set.

  @{"Solomon" LINK "Solomon"}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Solomon"

Solomon

This is an old style Hebrew Font.

Font Formats: - @{"Adobe" LINK "Adobe"} (Type 1 [pfa & pfb], Type 3, Bitmap)
              - @{"DMF" LINK "DMF"} (+ bitmap)
              - @{"Bitmap" LINK "Bitmap"} (Black&White & Colour [8 Colours])
              - @{"IntelliFont" LINK "IntelliFont"}

Font ID:      11060

Directory:    Non-Latin/Hebrew/Solomon

This font is freeware. Copyright © 1994 by @{"Danny Amor" LINK "Danny Amor"}.
